https://kyverno.io/policies/

If you want to apply anything on the cluster level lets say you want restrict a image that don't want to utilize by the k8 pod or by default pod need to have stable cpu & memory then "kyverno" will be vert helpful.

Note: Its applicated for entire cluster level where as resource quota and limit range will applicable on Namespace level.

Ex: https://kyverno.io/policies/other/add-default-resources/add-default-resources/

